---
description: Run Agent Coordinator context inject before starting a Cursor agent
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

Before starting an agent in this project, run coordinator context so the
agent sees shared state:

```bash
node .agent-coordinator/hooks/cursor.js
```

Equivalent: `npx coordinator context inject cursor`

When you change a shared state value, record it:

```bash
coordinator state set <KEY> <OLD> <NEW> --tool cursor --reason "<why>"
```
